<div class="mmooc-power-functions">
  <h1 class="xl">Power Functions</h1>
  <h2>Create groups</h2>
  <p><a href="/?mmpf">Back</a></p>

  <form>
    <dl>
      <dt><label for="account">Choose the account</label></dt>
      <dd>
        <select name="account">
          {{#accounts}}
            <option value="{{id}}">{{name}}</option>
          {{/accounts}}
        </select>
      </dd>
      <dt><label for="Category">Choose the account</label></dt>
      <dd>
        <select name="category">
            <option value="">...</option>
        </select>
      </dd>
      <dt><label for="csv">Upload CSV file</label></dt>
      <dd><input type="file" name="csv"></dd>
    </dl>
    <input type="submit"/>
  </form>

  <div class="side-information">
    <h3>Decription of CSV format</h3>
    <p>First line of the file must be the name of the columns. Column separators are commas.
    <dl>
      <dt>name [String]
      <dd>The name of the group
      <dt>description [String]
      <dd>A description of the group
      <dt>is_public [Boolean]
      <dd>whether the group is public (applies only to community groups)
      <dt>join_level [String]
      <dd>“parent_context_auto_join” | “parent_context_request” | “invitation_only”
      <dt>storage_quota_mb [Integer]
      <dd>The allowed file storage for the group, in megabytes. This
        parameter is ignored if the caller does not have the
        manage_storage_quotas permission.
    </dl>
  </div>
</div>
